metadata.description: The Party Poms are a collection of 5,454 unique Party Pom NFTs - distinct digital collectible assets living on the Ethereum blockchain. Party Pom members gain access to one-of-a-kind in-person intimate private concerts with festival-grade audio/visual across the United States. Party Poms also receive preferential treatment at events with perks that can include open bar, VIP section and DJ stage access, and performer meet and greets.
